{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_shu_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_shu_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"谓我何求","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"在一尊古老的神农塑像前，黍与一位年轻的农业天师学徒聊起了这位传说中的人物。一介凡人，究竟何以完成那些名垂青史的壮举？","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_shu_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["禾生","黍","质朴的农人","懵懂的少女","年迈的女性"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_bg_47_g12_cityoperastage.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":5},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_frmrwkhrd","id":6},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":7},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_frmrwkhrd","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":9},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_frmrwkhrd","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":11},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowbootwalk","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"你是谁......？","id":14},{"type":"text","text":"你是从哪里来的？","id":15},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"没有来处，没有亲人，也不知道自己是谁......","id":17},{"type":"text","text":"难不成，你是故事里的神仙？","id":18},{"type":"dialog","id":19},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":20},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":21},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"5","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_brdchrp","volume":"1","id":23},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_calm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":24,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":25},{"type":"text","text":"惊蛰。","id":26},{"type":"text","text":"入春连下了好几天雨，天气终于放晴。","id":27},{"type":"text","text":"广场中央是一座方方正正的台子——像是戏台，又像是祭坛，上面有一尊塑像默然伫立。","id":28},{"type":"text","text":"塑像的造型是一位衣着古朴的女性，看不清五官，只能看出她在远远望着什么。","id":29},{"type":"text","text":"少年小心翼翼地将一株青翠的秧苗供奉到塑像前，恭敬地鞠了一躬。","id":30},{"type":"dialog","id":31},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#3$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":32},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"神农保佑......","id":34,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"今年一定要顺顺利利......","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"charslot","id":38},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":39},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","duration":"1","id":40},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"老师？","id":44,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a7/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"我还在找你，让你准备的土壤样本呢——你在这做什么？","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我......","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"少年侧着身子，想要挡住身后刚刚献上的“贡品”。","id":49},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"过两天就是下秧的日子了，今年是我第一次独立负责一块试验田，我心里实在没底......怕碰上意外，也怕自己做不好。","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我听天师府的前辈说，这种时候，他们都会来这里拜拜......我是新入学的学徒，神农说不定还会额外关照点......","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4b/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"那些为老不尊的，都给年轻人教些什么......","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"碰上意外，就不种田啦？","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......","id":61,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/29/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":62},{"type":"charslot","id":63},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":64},{"type":"text","text":"连着几日刮风下雨，不会说话的塑像沾了一身泥土，就像是刚结束了地里劳作的样子。","id":65},{"type":"text","text":"女性走上前，轻轻擦拭着塑像。","id":66},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"“神农”在这里勤勤恳恳耕耘了一辈子，倒是被你们供成了一个神仙，凡事都盼着她来帮你们解决。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......也只有遇到解决不了的问题、过不去的坎，大家才会想起来看看她。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/38/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"老师......您说，真的有“神农”这么一个人吗？","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a7/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"怎么这么问？","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"在一千年前，制定历法，划分了二十四节气......还在一片满是危险的土地上开垦出这么一大片的田地。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我实在没办法想象，这些都是一个人能做到的事......","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"不管你相不相信，天上的时节流转，脚下的土地变迁，都是骗不了人的。","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"一定是有人先做了这些事，才有的这些故事。","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"到底是什么样的人，才能做成这些事......？","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a7/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"她啊......就是一个没什么心眼的笨人罢了。","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/38/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":87},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":88},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"charslot","id":90},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":91},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bf/Avg_bg_40_g2_glacier.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":92},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":93},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":94},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":95,"musicid":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":96},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","duration":"1.5","id":97},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"从高处看这片大地是什么样的？","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"什么......？","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"你说，你曾经的身体比山还要高，天上飘着的云够不到你的肩膀——那你看到的风景是什么样的？","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"你们看到的这连绵不绝的山，在我眼里就像有些起伏的土坡；你们看到的参天大树，在我眼里就和这路边的秧苗差不多。","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"枯山死水，万年如此。","id":106},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"那你是不是也看不清地上的这些花草树木，听不清羽兽啼叫？","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"那确实太寂寞了点......","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"你就不怕我？","id":112,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"怕什么？你长得和我们一样，又不像妖怪。","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"可我和你们到底还是不一样，我的寿命是你们的千百倍，我要是生起气来，随便一挥手，你们全都要灰飞烟灭。","id":116,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"噗——","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"你还敢笑......","id":120,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"我也听过那些神话故事，故事里的神仙都是寂寞无聊了才跑来人间的。","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"如果不是孤单得受不了，你为什么要变成人的模样跑出来？你让我“灰飞烟灭”了，你又该找谁说话去？","id":124,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"我才不是——","id":126,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"......","id":128,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"唉，有这样的力量，为什么要打打杀杀的呢？","id":130,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"我要是有那么庞大的身体，我就允许人们在我身上种庄稼、种果蔬！对了，你是不是也可以让庄稼长得更好？","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"这有什么难的，我现在就能做到......就像这样。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":135},{"type":"charslot","id":136},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_lmrgcwnd","volume":"1","id":137},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":138},{"type":"text","text":"少女轻轻挥手，地里一株青色的高粱苗眨眼间成熟，结出了沉甸甸的谷实。","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"只要我愿意，我可以让这整片雪原都变成农田。","id":140},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"......","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"农人瞪大了眼，半天说不出话来。","id":143},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"你这样做，会很累吗？","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"没什么大不了的，总比你们慢腾腾地种田来得轻松。","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"那你会向我们要什么回报？","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"我能向你们要什么？我只是心情好，就随手这么做了。","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"那......","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"不不......你还是不要这样做比较好。","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"我不能只顾着眼前，你现在心情不错，帮我们做了这些事，要是哪天心情不好，说不定就离开了。","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"现在大伙依赖你的神力，可将来你离开了，这里的庄稼岂不是也要消失？那时候人们不会自己种庄稼，又得饿肚子。","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"我们还是老老实实地自己开荒种地，心里踏实点。","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"......我也遇到过其他不少人，见我显露了一星半点的能力，就都巴不得求我施舍他们点什么。","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"可是像你这样，就算到你死了，才能开垦多少地？","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"能开垦多少算多少，只要自己尽力就好啦。我做不完的事，之后还会有人接着做的。","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"你这不是自相矛盾？一会说“不能只顾眼前”，一会又说“尽力就好”。","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"矛盾吗？人又不能像神仙一样心想事成，只能做自己能做的，然后带着点念想活着。很普通，心里也很踏实......","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"很踏实？","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"嗯......给。","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":176},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":177},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":178},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"这是干什么？","id":180,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"我学不会你们神仙种地的法子，但我可以教你我们人类种地的法子。慢是慢了点，但也是管用的。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"等你学会了人种地的办法，说不定也就能体会“人”的心情了。","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":185},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":186},{"type":"charslot","id":187},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":188},{"type":"text","text":"做“人”，辛苦吗？","id":189},{"type":"dialog","id":190},{"type":"sticker","id":191,"multi":"true","text":"当然辛苦啦！你看我手上这些冻疮......我年纪轻轻的，下雨天的时候已经会腰疼了。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":192},{"type":"text","text":"我可以带你去别的地方，风景如画，四季如春。不用你辛苦劳作，那里的东西保证你十辈子都吃不完。","id":193},{"type":"dialog","id":194},{"type":"sticker","id":195,"multi":"true","text":"哈哈，我就知道！你还是怕孤单，想找人陪你玩是不是？","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":196},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":197},{"type":"dialog","id":198},{"type":"sticker","id":199,"multi":"true","text":"不过，还是算了。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":200},{"type":"text","text":"你不相信我？","id":201},{"type":"dialog","id":202},{"type":"sticker","id":203,"multi":"true","text":"我当然信。这片大地那么大，肯定有好些我没去过的好地方......可是我也害怕，怕我见过那么好的地方，就再也不想回来了。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":204},{"type":"sticker","id":205,"multi":"true","text":"人这一辈子太短啦，能种好眼前这些庄稼，我就心满意足了。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":206},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":207},{"type":"dialog","id":208},{"type":"sticker","id":209,"multi":"true","text":"不过，想让我陪你出去玩也不是不行，除非......","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":210},{"type":"sticker","id":211,"multi":"true","text":"除非你答应我，能让这世上所有人，以后都能吃饱肚子。","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":212},{"type":"dialog","id":213},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":214},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":215},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":217},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"false","id":218},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_frmrwkhrd","id":219},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":220},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"false","id":221},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_frmrwkhrd","id":222},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"哼哼......♪","id":224,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"你好像很开心？","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"当然啦！","id":228,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ad/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"你看，试种在这里的种子顺利长出来啦，我们又多了一种能用来果腹的庄稼。","id":230,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"再过几年，我们把这一片荒原开垦成田地，种出来的粮食又可以多供给几个村子的人了。","id":232,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"你说的那些人——你认识他们？","id":234,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"不......不认识呀。","id":236,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"那你为什么要在意他们？","id":238,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5e/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"唔......关爱别人，互帮互助，难道不是理所应当的事？","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"你在这里劳作，自给自足，他们帮你什么了？","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"眼下或许是帮不到，但是将来......","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"所以你给他们提供粮食，是为了将来换取回报？","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"倒也不能这么说......唉！都被你问糊涂了。","id":248,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"......我也很糊涂。","id":250,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"我记得看过先贤写的书，上面有一句话叫“民胞物与”，大概是说，人应该要关爱身边的人，还有一切花草树木。","id":252,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/91/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"我嘴笨，说不出个道理。就是觉得眼前的花草树木很好看，就想多种一点；饿肚子的滋味不好受，就不想让别人也体会这种感觉。","id":254,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"唉......你是神仙，肯定不知道饿肚子的滋味，可难受啦......","id":256,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"那是什么感觉？","id":258,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"肚子很疼，五脏六腑好像拧在一起似的疼。整个人浑身上下一丝力气都没有，坐着也不是躺着也不是，心里也跟着空落落的。","id":260,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"就像世上所有难过的事，都撞在同一天发生在你身上。","id":262,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"......那又是什么感觉？","id":264,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"比如......你最爱的亲人、最好的朋友离世了，你知道他们再也回不来了......","id":266,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"......","id":268,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"......","id":270,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a5/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"我还是不明白......","id":272,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a5/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"说是不明白，可你还是陪着我在这里待了这么久。","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"嗯，你陪着我的这些日子，我就很喜欢，有人陪我聊天，感觉干活都没那么辛苦了。","id":276,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"要是将来哪一天你不在了，我就会很难过，所以就会想办法让你在这里多待一会。","id":278,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"懵懂的少女","text":"......","id":280,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1242_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"质朴的农人","text":"唉，也不是一定要让你留下来的意思......我还记得，你说想要明白“人”是什么样的。","id":282,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_1242_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":283},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":284},{"type":"charslot","id":285},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":286},{"type":"dialog","id":287},{"type":"sticker","id":288,"multi":"true","text":"你现在，能感受到开心吗？","x":"300","y":"270","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","block":"true"},{"type":"sticker","id":289},{"type":"dialog","id":290},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_bg_47_g12_cityoperastage.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":291},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":292},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":294},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"您居然说“神农”是笨人......","id":296,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a7/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"有没有听这里上年纪的职农说过，收割庄稼的时候千万不要抬头看？","id":298,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你低着头，还有勇气割手头的庄稼，一旦抬头，对着望不到边的庄稼地，可就连路都走不动了。","id":300,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/38/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"人生短短几十年，哪有那么多工夫顾及生前身后事，只是盯好眼前一件事就够累人了。","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/38/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"但当你一门心思扑在一件事上，回过神的时候才会发现，不知不觉也已经走出去很远了。","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你猜，神农去世的时候，大荒城的田地有多大面积？","id":306,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"只有现在的一半？还是三分之一？","id":308,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"看到南边那片山坡了吗？当时开垦的田，就到那座山脚下。","id":310,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"只有......这么一点？","id":312,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a7/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"那时的条件远不比现在，别说这些源石装置了，人们打一把结实点的犁都很费劲。","id":314,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"山上的岩石挖不开，北边的冻土凿不动。所以南到那边的山坡，北到眼前的神农像，那时候的大荒城，就只有这么大。","id":316,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"这是哪里的记载，您为什么记得这么清楚？","id":318,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a7/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"是哪里的记载......我也忘了。","id":320,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/38/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"书上说，神农晚年的时候，一直想要向北开垦农田，最终也是病逝在了去北边找寻“神谷”的路上。","id":322,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"可为什么这尊神农像，却是面向南方的？","id":324,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"神农一生都在这里劳作，为的也只是能让她的同胞不再经受饥寒交迫。她最后放不下的，应该也是故乡的人吧。","id":326,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/38/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"她最后，应该也是在望着故乡吧。","id":328,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/38/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"对了老师，说起来，您又是为什么要当农业天师的？","id":330,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4b/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......在我很小的时候，我体会过一次饿肚子的感觉。从那以后，我就下定决心，不能让更多人，再经历那样的感觉。","id":332,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"原来老师您也经历过饥荒吗......","id":334,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a7/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"嗯......那也已经是很久以前的事了。","id":336,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"和神农一样啊......","id":338,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"大荒城还有许多职农，许多农业天师。大家或多或少，都有相似的理由吧。","id":340,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":341},{"type":"charslot","id":342},{"type":"text","text":"日头渐高，吹过的春风有了暖意，人身上也暖烘烘的。","id":343},{"type":"text","text":"云层被风推走，一缕阳光斜着照在塑像模糊的面庞上。","id":344},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"......","id":346,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4b/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"我突然在想，炎国有那么多神话传说，“神农”“挖山人”“炎”......","id":348,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4b/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"到现在我们也不知道到底是确有其人，还是神话故事。神农会不会，也不是“一个人”呢？","id":350,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4b/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"她不希望别人记得她是谁，她只是希望，有更多人去做和她一样的事，才会故意隐去名字和样貌。","id":352,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"只是这样一来，作为一个人，就真的没有人记得她了......","id":354,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"如果真的有这么一个人的话，她看到现在大荒城的模样，还会在意人们记不记得自己的名字吗？","id":356,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"又或许，她就是害羞，才不想留下名字和样貌吧。","id":358,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":359},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":360},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":361},{"type":"charslot","id":362},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":363},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bf/Avg_bg_40_g2_glacier.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":364},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":365},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":366},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":367,"musicid":2},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowstormflp","volume":"0.6","loop":"true","channel":"wind","id":368},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":369},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_snowbootwalk","id":370},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"呼......","id":372},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你再不乖乖回去，接下来几天的饭里就别想见到肉了。","id":374,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"黍......你不能这样欺负老人。","id":376,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"那就有点老人的样子。这个天气穿着一件单衣跑出来赏雪，你真是好雅兴。今天可是小寒。","id":378,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"我就知道，每到这个时节，腰就开始痛，真是一点不差......我哪里躺得住哟。","id":380,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"今年冬天这么冷，明年开春的时候，冻住的土地能及时化开吗......","id":382,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"那也不是你现在该操心的事，你再这样不顾身体，能不能看到明年春天还两说呢。","id":384,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"那可不行......我还打算等开春的时候，再去一次北边。上次在东北边的森林迷了路，这次就走西边的路。","id":386,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......你是存心气我。","id":388,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"等你入土了，我就叫人给你立一尊雕像摆在这，替你望着心心念念的北边。","id":390,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"那就再好不过啦。","id":392,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"可千万别按我现在的模样雕，丑死啦。","id":394,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"身上的衣服，就按你弟弟送我的那件衣服去做吧，我很喜欢。","id":396,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"哎，说起来，也有好几年没见过他了。也不知道，最后还能不能再见上他一面......","id":398,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"时间过得真快哟......就好像昨天才刚遇到你一样。这几十年，就这么过去了。","id":400,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"这几十年，大荒城的田地变大了两倍，每年的庄稼产量也翻了不止一倍......大家都管你叫“神农”，你就知足吧。","id":402,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"人啊，总是贪心，哪有知足的时候。","id":404,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"有了一年能种两季的稻子，就想要三季稻；有了一百亩的田，就想要两百亩......","id":406,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"等到哪天我坐在这里，一眼都望不到大荒城的头，我就想，能不能去你说过的，那个风景如画、四季如春的地方。","id":408,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"好啊，等你养好了病，明年一开春，我就带你去。","id":410,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"你又在骗我......你每次说谎的时候，都会用力眨一下眼睛，我早就发现啦。","id":412,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/34/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......","id":414,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"黍......你该知道，总有这么一天的。","id":416,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"当然，我不是对你讲过，在遇见你之前，我早就见惯了。","id":418,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/38/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"生老病死，万物法则......","id":420,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"我......","id":422,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"你现在，感受到了吗？","id":424,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":425},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你说什么？","id":426,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"像“人”一样......","id":428,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"会为一件极小的事情高兴，会为明知道结果的事情难过，会有期待，有不舍......","id":430,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"我能感受到你的情绪......人就是因为这一点共同的情绪，才联系在一起的。","id":432,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你用了一辈子才教会我一件事......实在算不上个好老师。","id":434,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"所以我走了以后，你可以替我留在这里吗？","id":436,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"不需要你来当这里的守护神，只是作为一个人，生活在这里。","id":438,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"把我们琢磨出来的那些种地的办法，教给那些年轻的孩子，你那么聪明，肯定教得比我好......","id":440,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/63/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"......","id":442,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"他们会记得，曾经有一个人，只是为了让她的同胞吃饱饭，就把一辈子都花在了这片天寒地冻的雪原上。","id":444,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"我哪里是一个人，明明有一个神仙，装成人的样子，陪了我这么久。","id":446,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"但是没关系，你和我们过着一样的生活，没有人知道你是偷偷跑入人间的神仙。","id":448,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"虽然我看不到了，但或许有一天，大荒城也可以变成你说的那样的地方......那时，会有很多人陪你一起看风景，你应该就不会孤独了吧。","id":450,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":451},{"type":"dialogue","name":"年迈的女性","text":"来年那边山坡上迎春花开的时候，你能帮我编个花环吗？","id":452,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":453},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":454},{"type":"charslot","id":455},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"wind","fadetime":"2","id":456},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":457},{"type":"dialog","id":458},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/16/Avg_bg_47_g12_cityoperastage.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":459},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":460},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":461},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":462},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":463},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"老师，时间不早了。我先去准备下秧用的东西了。","id":464,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4b/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#13$1","focus":"m","id":465},{"type":"dialogue","name":"禾生","text":"不管今年年成怎么样，我都会尽力......","id":466,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5c/Avg_avg_4119_wanqin_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":467},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"嗯，你去吧。","id":468,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":469},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":470},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":471},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":472},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":473},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":474},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":475},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你看，他们都还记得你呢。","id":476,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_2025_shu_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":477},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黍","text":"你一副淡泊名声的样子，倒是让别人惦记了你一千年......让我说你什么好。","id":478,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/79/Avg_avg_2025_shu_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":479},{"type":"charslot","id":480},{"type":"text","text":"羽兽衔来一朵黄色的小花，落在塑像的斗笠上。","id":481},{"type":"text","text":"它像是选中了一处筑巢的好地方，又接二连三地衔来好几朵带枝的花朵。不一会，黄色的花朵便覆满了帽檐。","id":482},{"type":"text","text":"怪他去后花如许，记得来时路也无。","id":483},{"type":"dialog","id":484},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":485},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":486},{"type":"charslot","id":487},{"type":"image","id":488}],"characters":["禾生","黍","质朴的农人","懵懂的少女","年迈的女性"]}